                  <additions>
                     <p>Marginalia: The copy has been collated with the exemplar by the copyist. He has entered corrections in the margins (sometimes marked with صح). An owner named <persName key="person_f102">Abu al-Fada'il Abu Sa'id al-Arzaq</persName> wrote his reading record (طالع [read]) on <date calendar="#Hijri-qamari">Saturday, 4th of Ḏū al-Ḥijja, 708H</date> (see colophone 2) in a different, darker black ink. He also has entered many correction in the margines (marked with صح), and has noted variant readings from another manuscript (marked with خ [i.e., نسخة]).</p>
